Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:37.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96034,97702}– Bye!\N– No breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:41.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97952,101247}No, thanks! I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.46,0:01:49.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106461,109339}That hurts!\NWatch where you're driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.58,0:01:52.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109589,112634}– I'm sorry.\N– Oh, really! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113551,115511}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:02:00.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118556,120308}Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:02.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120933,122518}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:10.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127148,130568}Please accept our deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:14.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132320,134947}I'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137116,139369}Master Ryutaro, she forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:23.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139911,143623}I'm almost positive\Nit's a St. Paulia School hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143873,145041}I've found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:31.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146417,151047}MEIMI IS ENGAGED\NTO A MULTI-MILLIONAIRE'S SON!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:41.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157053,161808}– Don't be depressed about being tardy.\N– Sister's lecture is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:43.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162058,163810}Good, if that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:47.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164060,167897}It might be the Board Chairman\Nwho will give you a lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:51.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168147,171150}You're kidding!\NI was only late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171401,174821}Meimi! Please come\Nto the Chairman's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175029,176739}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181577,183996}Don't you think something's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:08.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184247,188042}– Oh, it's you, Saruwatari.\N– The name's Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188292,189794}What's so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:14.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190044,194424}Do you think you'd be called to\Nthe Chairman's office for being tardy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:18.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194674,198636}– Who knows?\N– I think this is gonna be a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:25.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202348,205643}– Meimi, come here.\N– Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206728,209522}I'm very sorry!\NI was tardy because a car—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:34.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209731,214110}She's the one! No mistake!\NShe's the one I've been looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214360,215611}You're—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:40.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216362,220867}I'm very sorry about this morning.\NMy name is Ryutaro Tomikoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:45.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221534,225997}This morning you dropped your hat.\NThis gentleman came to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226247,228458}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228666,231169}And also it's very sudden…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:55.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231377,235840}…but Mr. Tomikoji requests that\Nhe be given the chance to date you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236215,238342}Date? With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238885,240845}This meeting is a God-given destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:05.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241053,245016}Love at first sight is\Nwhat you'd call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:08.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245266,248019}It's all so sudden and…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:13.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248269,253983}Meimi, if you accept, we shall\Nforget the tardy incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254484,256944}Well, he's a most courteous young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:21.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257153,261407}To go out of his way for permission\Nto date one of our students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261657,262992}You're correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:26.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263534,266496}Everyone tells me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269165,271167}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271375,272794}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:37.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273044,277840}I was sure you'd give that reply.\NWell, it's time we leave for our date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:42.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278090,282094}Please take good care\Nof our Meimi. And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:47.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282553,287558}Regarding the contribution, I will\Nhave a company employee prepare it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287809,289018}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:52.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289268,292021}Contribution? I've been sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:57.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293147,297443}– Then we'll be back.\N– Have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301405,303616}Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306494,307954}It's a scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:14.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311123,314544}A simple park like this\Ncan be quite refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314794,317255}I couldn't think of anywhere\Nfor a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:20.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317505,320383}I think your pureness is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322301,325179}That's it!\NI should ask him for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:28.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325429,328349}Then he'd be convinced\Nto forget this date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328724,331644}– I've thought of something!\N– Wherever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:36.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331894,336399}I'd like to eat at Tetsujin-tei\Nand go to a musical at Bayside Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:41.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336649,341279}– Let's not forget Wonderland Garden.\N– OK. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:53.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351414,353249}What a long line!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:57.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353958,357253}Meimi, what's the matter?\NThe entrance is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358337,360798}But we've got to stand in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:07.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364135,367722}We came in without standing in line.\NAre you sure it's OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:12.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367930,372435}Mother is sponsor of this restaurant\Nso we can come in anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372685,375688}I see. Ryutaro, your mother\Nis quite a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:20.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376147,380902}Yes. After Father's death, she's been\Nrunning the company by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381152,383404}But she does too much\Nwhen it comes to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:28.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383654,388659}Like deciding my fiancee.\NI'd like to decide on my own fiancee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:33.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389076,393289}– You're right.\N– Well, the musical is next, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:38.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393539,398210}Yes. Could you possibly be sponsors\Nof the Bayside Hall as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:41.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399086,401047}You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:46.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401255,406260}But Mother has special reserved seats\Nso there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:50.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406510,410264}This guy has no idea\Nwhat standing in line is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410514,412642}– Shall we go?\N– Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:56.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413517,416312}My parents will be worried\Nif I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416562,417647}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:02.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417897,422735}Next time, we'll get permission\Nfrom your parents and enjoy our date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422985,424528}I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:08.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424779,428074}Don't worry. I can get home\Nby myself. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:12.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428783,432036}Meimi! You're shy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:20.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435623,440002}This is the fourth day. No matter\Nwhat Sister says, I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440252,442463}Meimi, don't be such a spoilsport!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:26.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442672,446384}She's right. You get to go\Nto all the popular places.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:31.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446634,451222}It's God's teachings. That's what you\Nget for accepting a date so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:35.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451764,455768}Oh, Seira. I'm leaving from\Nthe back gate so he won't catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456018,458187}I'm leaving the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:48.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463776,468114}Young lady, we've been waiting\Nfor you. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469323,470616}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:57.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474620,477581}Is something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:01.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478541,481544}If you're OK with it,\NI'd be glad to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:07.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481794,487717}Someone switched the heirloom necklace\Nmy mother left me with a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491637,494849}– This is it.\N– What? This shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495558,497852}Mother is the sponsor\Nof this boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498102,500062}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:25.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500312,505234}– I'd like to select something for you.\N– You don't have to buy me clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:29.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505484,509572}You're meeting my mother,\Nso please be conscious of your dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509822,511032}Meet your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:35.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511574,515161}Yes. Tomorrow evening,\NMother's having a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:38.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515411,518039}I want to introduce you\Nas my fiancee there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518247,521959}Fiancee? You can't do that!\NI have no intentions to—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522209,524420}I'm still a junior high student!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:49.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524628,529508}You didn't hear the Chairman? I'm\Ndating you with intentions to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529759,532636}I've heard nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534472,535723}It's a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538434,540644}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:08.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544774,548736}– The news is all over the class!\N– Is it true he proposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548986,551655}He's the son of the owner\Nof the Tomikoji Group!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551947,554033}How do all of you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:17.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554283,557369}Looks like the source of the news\Nis from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:21.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557620,561582}Asuka Jr., have you seen it?\NIt's my greatest scoop! Hey, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561999,564668}Be quiet!\NAre you a show business reporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564919,566128}Don't get so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566378,569298}– I said, be quiet, Saruwatari!\N– It's Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:32.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569548,572760}If you don't like Saruwatari,\Nhow about Sawagani?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:38.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573135,578057}That's jealousy.\NHey, Meimi, Miss Popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:45.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581769,585397}Meimi, I'm sorry to disturb you\Nwhen you're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:49.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585648,589610}Oh, Seira, you too! Don't be mean.\NIt's work, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:53.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590236,593114}The job is for Miss Yumi Imamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:57.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593364,597910}She was a secretary for that\Nwoman entrepreneur, Madam Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:01.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598160,601330}But Madam Ranko has switched…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:05.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601539,605334}…her mother's heirloom necklace\Nwith a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:07.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606335,607628}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:12.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608003,612716}President, this isn't the necklace\Nthat I left with you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613342,615970}What in the world\Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616220,618639}Are you saying\NI replaced it with a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618889,622643}I know the real one.\NPlease give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622852,624562}Stop this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:28.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624812,628691}If you don't trust me,\Nthen you don't have to work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628899,631235}Leave here at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:35.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631527,635823}Yumi, who complained to Madam Ranko,\Nlost her job as secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636073,638242}What a terrible woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638868,641996}I understand.\NJust leave things to St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642246,644498}This is the fake necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:48.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644748,648836}It seems that Madam Ranko always\Nhas the real one on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:53.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649086,653340}And your only chance is the party\Nthat's being held tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653591,656010}Wait, tomorrow's party?\NIs it…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:11:01.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656594,661223}Right. Madam Ranko's real name\Nis Ranko Tomikoji…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661473,663225}…Ryutaro's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:08.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664393,668731}The party tomorrow will include\Nforeign diplomats and other VIPs…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668981,671817}…so the security will be\Nquite tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672067,673736}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:19.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674153,679158}I think the best way to get in is\Nto go to that party with Ryutaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:23.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679408,683287}Seira! Do you know what\Ngoing to that party means?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:26.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683495,686624}I won't! I'll get in there\Non my very own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687416,689335}Meimi.
Comment: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:29.71,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:689710,689710}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:34.71,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:694715,694715}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:45.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702139,705976}Hey, Asuka Jr.! Kick the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:49.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706936,709438}Sure. Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:06.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722368,726914}Tonight at the party hall, I'll be\Npicking up Madam Ranko 's necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727456,729416}A notice from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729667,731252}Hey, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731794,734797}What are you going\Nto do about this ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738133,740219}– I'm home!\N– Welcome home, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:22.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740469,742680}Welcome home. I'll get tea for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742930,745641}Thanks, but, Mama…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:30.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746809,750854}It's beautiful!\NI've always wanted one like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:36.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752189,756860}OK, you're getting sleepy.\NOne, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:42.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759071,762283}Wow! Papa, is this hypnotism?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:45.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762533,765327}But it's still in the research stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:49.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765577,769623}All right, when I count to three,\Nyou'll become a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769873,772793}One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778215,780509}I'd say it's quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:05.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780718,785222}When I count to three, you'll\Nreturn to normal. Three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786724,788809}What? I…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:12.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789059,792021}Mother, you were a cat a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792271,794773}You used me as a guinea pig,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:19.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795024,799403}– I'm sorry. Here's the pendant.\N– You won't get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:22.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799653,802364}– Forgive me!\N– No, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:26.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803157,806243}Shall we go? We're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812791,815169}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:42.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818547,822301}I knew you'd come to the party\Nwithout telling your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822551,823677}Ryutaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:47.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823927,827431}Shall we go?\NBut that dress just won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:50.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827681,830184}– Old man, bring it to me.\N– Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830434,832644}What do you mean by "it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:57.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832853,837358}He'll bring the dress I selected\Nfor you, so please change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837608,838776}Young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843697,845199}Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:09.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846158,849495}Got no choice.\NI'll have to do as Seira said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:12.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849703,852206}Plus, that's a nice dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:23.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858420,863550}I don't need the security. As you\Nca n see, I have the necklace on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:28.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863801,868013}But St. Tail is able\Nto steal from anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:32.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868389,872935}As I've said, that is why\Nwe've hired our own security guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:37.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873185,877481}Also, to have you roam around\Ndressed like that is a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878232,881985}I don't mind if you do your security\Nbut do it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882236,884947}Please wait! I'm not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889118,890411}Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901004,902339}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905092,907302}– Meimi.\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908262,909555}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:24.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918981,924069}Meimi. He really proposed to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936540,938917}That woman over there is my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:42.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940627,942171}That's the necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942421,943547}– Meimi.\N– Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:46.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943755,946592}Let's have one dance\Nbefore I introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:51.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946800,951638}– No, thanks. I can't dance.\N– I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:59.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955225,959563}– Meimi, you're quite good.\N– Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959813,962441}Where's Madam Ranko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964151,965277}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965527,969031}Ryutaro, I feel a bit ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969281,971158}Would you like a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:15.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971408,975370}No, don't worry. I'll be fine\Nwith a bit of fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977372,978790}Wonder if she's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:34.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990844,994765}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:41.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999853,1001772}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003065,1005067}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:49.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006401,1009404}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:06.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023377,1026838}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029007,1031426}– What's this?\N– Where's the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031677,1033595}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:19.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037349,1039393}My necklace is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039643,1041353}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041603,1043772}She's appeared! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:28.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044022,1048277}– It's St. Tail!\N– Hurry! Hurry! Get it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048819,1051029}Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051780,1054658}I'll be leaving with the necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:41.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059454,1061415}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061873,1064751}…Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067170,1068672}…Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:55.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073176,1075220}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:18:00.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076930,1080142}Darn it! I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081435,1082936}Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:08.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085188,1088984}Wait! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:12.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089234,1092779}I'm the one\Nwho's gonna catch St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094865,1096366}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:21.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097200,1101121}Oh, boy. Why is Ryutaro here?\NThat's it. It'd be just right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:30.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107169,1110297}Miss St. Tail,\NI'd like to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:37.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115510,1117179}One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122142,1124436}Take this fake back to your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124686,1127606}St. Tail, you won't escape this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:56.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1134029,1136573}Asuka Jr., please take care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:58.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137074,1138575}What a dirty trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:01.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139159,1141912}Three, two, one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146541,1149753}Rats! What a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:26.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163183,1166520}Take good care of this memory\Nof your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:29.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1166770,1169481}Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171858,1173151}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:39.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173944,1179074}Ryutaro! You got it back\Nfor me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179866,1181576}She doesn't know it's fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:45.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181827,1185080}As a reward, I'll do\Nanything you want me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:50.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185330,1190043}Really? Then I don't want to marry\Nthe person you decided on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190293,1193255}You're not introducing me\Nto your mother now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:57.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193797,1197008}I want to marry St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:03.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1198051,1203557}Her long, graceful movements.\NBeautiful hair. Her long, slim legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203807,1206977}Meeting her is a God-given destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:11.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208979,1211189}Young lady, I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:16.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212524,1216194}Looks like Master Ryutaro's got\Nthat illness again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216737,1220782}So, what's everybody\Ngonna say about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:27.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223785,1227622}Yumi was very happy that\Nthe necklace was returned to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:32.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227831,1232210}Hey! Too bad about\NMr. Prince Charming, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:37.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232461,1237174}Oh, cut it out! Love at first sight\Nis a big pain in the butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:40.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237382,1240051}Sorry, sorry.\NWell, I'm going on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:43.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240719,1243472}Asuka Jr. seems to be in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243722,1245682}Sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:48.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245932,1248101}It's nice to see him smiling again.
